{"tid":1885750,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蔡英文外交斡旋　菲律賓宣佈解封台灣","createTime":"2020-02-18T13:20:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-18T13:45:34.000Z","uid":261647,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"3fcfc4280a99c89cd7a05c8656583116f325eabf","tid":1885750,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T13:20:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/ichentsai.md/photos/a.594024550667081/2722155837853931/?type=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fichentsai.md%2Fphotos%2Fa.594024550667081%2F2722155837853931%2F%3Ftype%3D3&d=aTFRN7Q3AKWWv%2B0RVwuGmp1QB7Ma9ovE6nvZW%2BRTqP4%3D&h=da4c0e27\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/ichentsai.md/photos/a.594024550667081/2722155837853931/?type=3</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NZqgcpR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNZqgcpR.png&h=8aa489dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n菲律賓之前在 2/2 時，對中港澳居民發佈禁令，禁止進入菲律賓，但到了前幾天，忽然說，因為臺灣也是中國的一部份，所以臺灣也在禁令實施範圍，臺灣人不能入境菲律賓！<br />\n <br />\n然後我國外交系統展開交涉，並有風聲傳出，不排除採取反制措施，例如考慮禁止菲律賓人來台工作。<br />\n <br />\n然後禁令就拿掉了。<br />\n <br />\n菲律賓並對外宣稱，因為臺灣嚴格的防疫措施，武漢肺炎控制良好，所以禁令不包括臺灣。"},{"pid":"57c74e011d01bbf5ad32916c9048e73b1d3455d6","tid":1885750,"uid":149383,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T13:20:29.000Z","msg":"成績表發放<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家唔該繼續report 藍絲youtube<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n打緊仗 唔該大家 打醒十二分精神<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KeLkjxq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKeLkjxq.png&h=9ea696e0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"957b8da85f39ee5c56d321ff8b994c7c4aba92f1","tid":1885750,"uid":127929,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T13:35:56.000Z","msg":"蔡英文哈哈哈哈.jpg"},{"pid":"be3b491203ad616b7114a961cd95d3a489969768","tid":1885750,"uid":6103,"like":0,"dislik